  <div class="description">
    <p>If it feels bothersome for you<br>
    to carry the attendance sheets<br>
    to every class,</p>
    <p>or if you can’t take attendance every class<br>
    due to the sheer number of student<br>
    yet you see the attendance rate drop<br>
    as the semester goes on,</p>
    <p><span class="bold">use the Attendance function.</span><br>
    <span class="smallfont">(Automatic attendance check will be done in 1 minute)</span></p>
  </div>
  <div class="spacer70"></div>
  <div>
