  <div class="explanation">
    <div>
      <img class="screenshot" src="https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/bttendancedevelop/Tutorial/ImageEN/1.png">
      <div class="spacer35"></div>
      <p>Press the Attendance button<br>on the course screen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="spacer74"></div>
    <div>
      <img class="screenshot" src="https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/bttendancedevelop/Tutorial/ImageEN/2.png">
      <div class="spacer35"></div>
      <p>Choose to take attendance<br>automatically using Bluetooth<br>or manually by calling<br>each student’s name.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="spacer74"></div>
    <div>
      <img class="screenshot" src="https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/bttendancedevelop/Tutorial/ImageEN/3.png">
