      <p>If you chose to take attendance<br>automatically using Bluetooth,<br>turn on the Bluetooth of<br>the instructor’s and the students’ smartphones.<br>Attendance will be automatically<br>taken and recorded.</p>
      <p>(Attention: Devices using iOS,<br>such as iPhones and iPads,<br>must have the application running<br>while the automatic attendance<br>check is underway.)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="spacer74"></div>
    <div>
      <img class="screenshot" src="https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/bttendancedevelop/Tutorial/ImageEN/4.png">
      <div class="spacer35"></div>
      <p>When taking attendance manually,<br>press each student’s name.<br>Pressing the name will toggle<br>the student’s attendance status<br>in the order of Absent -><br>Present -> Tardy -> Absent.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="spacer74"></div>
    <div>
      <img class="screenshot" src="https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/bttendancedevelop/Tutorial/ImageEN/5.png">
